text.tspan: MQM score is a weighted number of errors, with exceptions:
Majority segments thus have score of 0, some -1, -2, or -5.
MQM scores segments discretely with low noise.
DA scores segments continuously but is noisy.
ESA scores segments continuously with low noise.
